00:41:57.640 --> 00:41:59.800
No, yo no dije nada.

00:41:59.800 --> 00:42:01.040
Entonces quién…

00:42:03.280 --> 00:42:04.640
No culpes a Fang Mingfan.

00:42:04.680 --> 00:42:06.280
